Bernardine Flynn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernardine_Flynn 0 Bernardine Flynn (January 2, 1904 – March 20, 1977) was an American radio actress and announcer best known for playing the role of Sade Gook on the long-running comic radio serial Vic and Sade.
